data.description: New paint throughout. New photos coming soon. Don't miss your chance, these homes aren't available often.  You will enjoy the light that streams in through the large windows at the front and back of the house.  Hardwood floors greet you as you enter and carry you all the way to the kitchen where stone countertops and tile accentuate the gorgeous cabinetry.  You just won't believe how much space and storage this home offers with several closets.  Upstairs master bedroom is huge with a luxury en suite bathroom with plenty of windows.  The two additional bedrooms are across the hall and are connected by a Jack and Jill bath.  HVAC is approximately 4 years old, and roof is approximately 2 years old. And don't miss the fenced yard with workshop/storage building in the back. Home backs up to a nice area of trees to offer privacy, especially in the summer. Schedule you private tour today!
